<br>
2. They nerf manaburn (even though they said they wouldn't) and we still just stand there doing nothing.<br>
<br>
3. They give all casters the ability to crit hit on par with us nearly. Check out on raids, you often see mages and druids criting for 3k. Just the whole mage vs wizard thing stinks high heaven. <br>
<br>
4. Post 60 they dont give us any new pillar lines at all. Just useless Rains. <br>
<br>
5. Where are items with free nukes on them? Solists Icy Wand? Where are the upgrades except uber rare quests at 50th+ levels. <br>
<br>
