<br>
This isn't how the Druid/SK comunity are. They actually flame SOE/VI so they get stuff! We should get our act together and say &quot;NO VI, THY SHALL NOT NERF US FURTHER, NOW WE WANT STUFF BACK! ITS PAY BACK TIME!&quot;<br>
<br>
GIMME THE FRIKKIN STUFF I DESERVE! :-)<br>
<br>
